          "reviewBody": "CAGP is the best school I have seen ever. The care they give to the kids is simply outstanding. They emphasize hands on learning with individualized instruction to each kid which helps them in fostering independent learning and self directed exploration.\nThe school emphasizes imaginative play, nature exploration and rhythm in daily activities.",
