            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Sindhoori parent of kaashvi. i joined her in playschool (champs academy) when she was 2. she started to speak very fast. she learnt many new new things at that age itself. in play school she learnt months weeks alphabet shapes colors numbers alphabet rhymes stories everything.Teachers  espl priya mam and priyanka mam are very friendly and caring. every day she goes to school with great excitement. I was impressed with their coaching thatsy i continued my daughter  in the same school for prekg.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
